{"id": 7839, "source": "pestle", "subject": "chemistry", "course": null, "level": "SL", "paper": "1", "year": "2020", "session": "20N", "subtopic": "1-2-the-mole-concept", "title": "20N.1.SL.TZ0.3", "topic_id": "1", "source_url": "https://pestle.pages.dev/app/", "question_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Which of these molecular formulae are also empirical formulae?</span></p>\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: upper-roman;\">\n<li> <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">H</mi><mn>6</mn></msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">O</mi></math>\n</li>\n<li> <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi><mn>2</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">H</mi><mn>4</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">O</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math>\n</li>\n<li> <math class=\"wrs_chemistry\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi><mn>5</mn></msub><msub><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">H</mi><mn>12</mn></msub></math>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>A.  I and II only</p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">B.  I and III only<br/></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">C.  II and III only<br/></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">D.  I, II and III</span></p>\n</div>", "solution_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>B</p>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n<p>One of the best answered questions on paper 1. Very few of the candidates struggled with distinguishing molecular and empirical formula.</p>\n</div>"}